Hi Bill,

In second gear the lower part of the gear shift lever should be about 90 degrees to the floor in all directions.

If it still hits the hand brake and the hand brake comes out more than 6 clicks then adjust the hand brake!

good luck
Bob Wallace
Bristol UK
1998 T2

